text: David Pocock is a member of the Australian Senate, representing the Australian Capital Territory. He was elected in 2022.Senator David Pocock, Parliament of Australia, https://www.aph.gov.au/Senators_and_Members/Parliamentarian?MPID=256136 Pocock was born in Messina, South Africa, on 23 April 1988. He was a professional Rugby Union player from 2005 until 2020. He an independent politician, and is not a member of a political party. ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Australian rugby union players Category:Members of the Australian Senate
